1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,262
阿甘！
Gump!

2
00:00:01,335 --> 00:00:03,929
你到部队来干什么？
What's your sole purpose in this army?

3
00:00:04,005 --> 00:00:06,439
干你叫我干的事 教官！
To do whatever you tell me, Drill Sergeant!

4
00:00:06,508 --> 00:00:10,103
他妈的 阿甘 你他妈的真是个天才
God damn it, Gump, you're a goddamn genius.

5
00:00:10,179 --> 00:00:12,613
这是我听过的最了不起的回答
That's the most outstanding answer I've ever heard .

6
00:00:12,683 --> 00:00:15,277
你他妈的智商一定有一百六
You must have a goddamn I.Q Of 160.

7
00:00:15,353 --> 00:00:17,947
你他妈的真有天赋 列兵阿甘
You are goddamn gifted, Private Gump.

8
00:00:19,190 --> 00:00:21,454
大家都听着！
Listen up, people!

9
00:00:21,527 --> 00:00:24,462
不知什么原因 我很适合当兵
Now for some reason, I fit in the army

10
00:00:24,531 --> 00:00:26,465
就像一对插销那么适合
Like one of them round pegs.

11
00:00:26,533 --> 00:00:27,795
真实一点都不苦
It's not really hard.

12
00:00:27,868 --> 00:00:29,802
你只需把你的床铺好
You just make your bed neat,

13
00:00:29,870 --> 00:00:31,303
记着要站得笔直
remember to stand up straight,

14
00:00:31,372 --> 00:00:32,964
不管回答什么问题
and always answer every question

15
00:00:33,041 --> 00:00:34,975
都说“是 教官”
with "Yes, Drill Sergeant. "

16
00:00:35,043 --> 00:00:36,476
听清楚没有？
Is that clear?

17
00:00:36,546 --> 00:00:38,810
是 教官！
Yes, Drill Sergeant!

18
00:00:38,881 --> 00:00:42,317
你只需要沿着海底拖你的网
What you do is drag your nets along the bottom.

19
00:00:42,386 --> 00:00:43,648
在一个好天气
On a good day,

20
00:00:43,721 --> 00:00:46,656
你一次就能捕到上百磅的虾
you can catch over a hundred pounds of shrimp.

21
00:00:46,725 --> 00:00:47,987
如果一切顺利
Everything goes all right,

22
00:00:48,059 --> 00:00:49,822
两个人捕10个小时的虾
2 men shrimping 10 hours ,

23
00:00:49,895 --> 00:00:51,988
减去你用掉的油费
Less what you spends on gas...

24
00:00:52,064 --> 00:00:54,157
完成了 教官！
Done, Drill Sergeant!

25
00:00:54,234 --> 00:00:55,667
阿甘！
Gump!

26
00:00:57,238 --> 00:01:00,173
为什么你这么快就把枪装好了？
Why did you put that weapon together so quickly?

27
00:01:00,241 --> 00:01:02,175
你叫我这么做的 教官
You told me to, Drill Sergeant.

28
00:01:02,244 --> 00:01:03,836
耶稣基督啊
Jesus H. Christ.

29
00:01:03,912 --> 00:01:05,846
这是新的连队纪录
This is a new company record .

30
00:01:05,915 --> 00:01:07,348
如果不是因为
If it wasn't a waste

31
00:01:07,417 --> 00:01:08,850
我们这儿兵源不足
of a fine enlisted man,

32
00:01:08,918 --> 00:01:11,352
我会推荐你上军官预备学校 列兵阿甘
I'd recommend you for O.C.S., Private Gump.

33
00:01:11,422 --> 00:01:13,686
有朝一日你会当上将军！
You're going to be a general someday!

34
00:01:13,758 --> 00:01:15,692
现在把你的枪拆开重装一遍！
Now disassemble your weapon and continue!

35
00:01:17,763 --> 00:01:19,697
总之 就像我说过的
Anyway, like I was saying,

36
00:01:19,766 --> 00:01:22,030
虾是海里最好的东西
shrimp is the fruit of the sea.

37
00:01:22,101 --> 00:01:25,366
你可以烧它、煮它、烤它
You can barbecue it, boil it, broil it,

38
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,872
烘它、炒它
bake it, saute it.

39
00:01:26,941 --> 00:01:30,035
把它做成串烧虾、克洛虾
They's, uh, shrimp kabobs, shrimp creole,

40
00:01:30,111 --> 00:01:34,047
鲜虾羹、铁板虾、油炸虾
shrimp gumbo, pan fried, deep fried,

41
00:01:34,116 --> 00:01:35,378
脆皮虾
stir fried.

42
00:01:35,452 --> 00:01:37,215
还有菠萝虾
There's pineapple shrimp

43
00:01:37,287 --> 00:01:40,154
柠檬虾、椰子虾
and lemon shrimp, coconut shrimp,

44
00:01:40,224 --> 00:01:41,350
胡椒虾
pepper shrimp,

45
00:01:41,425 --> 00:01:43,859
鲜虾汤、油焖虾
shrimp soup, shrimp stew ,

46
00:01:43,929 --> 00:01:45,521
虾肉色拉
shrimp salad,

47
00:01:45,597 --> 00:01:47,360
土豆虾
shrimp in potatoes,

48
00:01:47,433 --> 00:01:48,866
虾肉汉堡包
shrimp burger,

49
00:01:48,935 --> 00:01:50,698
虾肉三明治
shrimp sandwich.

50
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:55,033
还有…差不多就这些了
That...That's about it.

